<item>
            <title>[PIG-3563] support adding archives to the distributed cache</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3563</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Support adding archives to the distributed cache by calling DistributedCacheFile.addCacheArchive instead of addCacheFile in JobControlCompiler.setupDistributedCache for common archive endings: .zip, .tgz, .tar.gz, .tar which are the extensions checked in downloadCacheObject in org.apache.hadoop.filecache.TrackerDistributedCacheManager&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12677735">PIG-3563</key>
            <summary>support adding archives to the distributed cache</summary>
